# Feature Completion Checklist (Mandatory)

**Authority:** `00_architecture_authority.mdc`

A feature is **NOT complete** unless every applicable item below is satisfied.

## Checklist

```
□ API           — /api/v1 endpoint in modules/<domain>/routes/, registered in mountVersionedApi.ts
□ Tenant        — tenant_id scoped; TenantRepository or explicit tenant filter; req.tenantId only
□ Audit         — withAudit() or recordDomainMutation() on mutations
□ Real-Time     — emitEntityEvent() after commit + client React Query invalidation / AppContext merge
□ Permissions   — shared/rbac permission + requirePermission() on route + usePermissions() in UI
□ LWW           — checkEntityLwwConflict() where entity has version; HTTP 409 on conflict
□ Reporting     — financial/report-facing changes use shared/ engines; report routes if new statements
□ Architecture  — no SQLite, no flat routes/services, no SQL in routes, no direct GL writes
```

## Agent behavior

Before marking a task complete, **explicitly confirm** each applicable checkbox in the response.

If the user asks to skip an item, explain the compliance risk and document the exception.

